Description: Python humanize utilities (Avalan PPA rebuild)
 humanize provides human-friendly representations of numbers, dates,
 file sizes and time deltas — for example "3 minutes ago", "1.2 MB",
 or "12 thousand". This rebuild ships the version Avalan pins (>= 4.12.3)
 because Ubuntu Noble carries an older release.
